        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Better Tools to Lower Costs Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill allows beneficiaries to qualify for low-income subsidies under the Medicare prescription drug benefit without having to meet certain resource requirements. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
